cs.DB, cs.CL, cs.DS, cs.LG, cs.CC. 

This paper deals with the evaluation of queries over text documents, which is a common problem in the field of databases (cs.DB). The use of regular expressions and automata also suggests a connection to natural language processing (cs.CL) and data structures (cs.DS). The analysis of complexity and computational hardness is a fundamental aspect of theoretical computer science (cs.CC), while the proposed syntactic constraints and ad-hoc compilation approach may involve machine learning techniques (cs.LG).
